---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="mt-24 border-t border-oastl-forest/20 bg-oastl-forest text-oastl-cream">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-4 text-sm">
    <div>
      <div class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase text-oastl-gold mb-2">OASTL</div>
      <p class="text-oastl-cream/80 leading-relaxed">
        Oregon Advocates for School Trust Lands. A 501(c)(3) nonprofit advocating for the State of Oregon's fiduciary duties to public schools under the 1859 Admissions Act. Affiliated with Advocates for School Trust Lands (ASTL) National.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase text-oastl-cream/60 mb-2">Governance</div>
      <p class="text-oastl-cream/80 leading-relaxed">
        OASTL is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit private foundation. IRS determination on file. Bylaws available on request. Volunteer board; members receive no compensation.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase text-oastl-cream/60 mb-2">Citation</div>
      <p class="text-oastl-cream/80 leading-relaxed">
        When citing OASTL materials, please use the case name <em>Advocates for School Trust Lands v. State of Oregon</em> and the date of access. Source documents are linked on the Legal Desk.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase text-oastl-cream/60 mb-2">Contact</div>
      <p class="text-oastl-cream/80 leading-relaxed">
        <a href="mailto:info@oastl.org" class="underline decoration-oastl-gold/60 hover:text-oastl-gold">info@oastl.org</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="border-t border-oastl-cream/10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-4 text-xs text-oastl-cream/60 italic text-center">
      Prototype build — imagery and design under iterative refinement. Final visual identity to be reviewed before broader release.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="border-t border-oastl-cream/10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-4 text-xs text-oastl-cream/50 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between gap-2">
      <span>© {year} Oregon Advocates for School Trust Lands. All rights reserved.</span>
      <span class="font-mono">oastl.org</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
